      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Lava Caverns Sweep",
        "Client": "Well-dressed Youth",
        "Description": "A great horde of monsters has\r\ngathered in the Lava Caverns,\r\nbut I must pass through! My\r\nguards and I cannot defeat\r\nthem, I know this\u2014but I also\r\nknow that a hunter as skilled\r\nas you can. Will you help us?",
        "Target": "Slay a total of 20 Uroktor or Rachnoid",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Grand m\u00E9nage aux Cavernes",
        "Client": "Jeune bien habill\u00E9",
        "Description": "Un gros groupe de monstres\r\ns\u0027est install\u00E9 aux Cavernes de\r\nlave, et moi je dois y aller !\r\nMes gardes et moi n\u0027arriverons\r\npas \u00E0 les \u00E9liminer, mais toi,\r\ntu pourrais ! Tu veux\r\nbien nous aider ?",
